text: Mangesh Panchal (born 27 December 1973) is an Indian-born Dutch One Day International cricketer. He made his debut for the Netherlands against Bermuda in August 2007. ==External links== * * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch cricketers Category:Netherlands One Day International cricketers Category:Indian emigrants to the Netherlands Category:Indian cricketers Category:Cricketers from Mumbai
